- When working under rslib/src/scheduler/, read rslib/src/scheduler/CLAUDE.md for local detail.
- FSRS vs SM-2 is a runtime branch on `BoolKey::Fsrs`; intervals and desired-retention flow through `fsrs.next_states(...)` in `answering/mod.rs`.
- The RPC contract is `proto/anki/scheduler.proto` — editing it needs a full `just check` (see proto/CLAUDE.md), not just `cargo check`.
